{"tid":1582654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買唔起蘋果pro都同我買份蘋果報，幫我買斷佢！","createTime":"2019-09-20T07:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:07:47.000Z","uid":316832,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4c26717ff6754307279f5ce1d6bf5dd0c6e66db8","tid":1582654,"uid":316832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"今日未買之前以為本特刊應該幾薄下<br />\n點知買完番黎本野鬼死咁厚，成55頁咁多<br />\n所有大大小小既事全部記錄晒<br />\n由6月至今蘋果一直被施壓但係依然無懼強權<br />\n你班連登仔仲唔幫手懲罰下蘋果日報！？<br />\n樓下間七仔已經比人買斷左，搞到我要行過去對面邨買，最離譜既竟然係對面邨仲有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔理你地買黎收藏好，貼堂定炆屎都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部人同我一人一份買斷全香港既蘋果，睇下佢仲敢唔敢咁大聲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AC9CV6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAC9CV6Z.jpg&h=62a28c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VsAHM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VsAHM1.jpg&h=cb9b633a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FH1Dko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FH1Dko.jpg&h=9d4925d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/20/145218_a4b97b5f84a7f4e6ffc7dd1e8479ae47.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F20%2F145218_a4b97b5f84a7f4e6ffc7dd1e8479ae47.jpeg&h=c7c96f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/20/145222_11c6099c10fc2ed7207bcae46a7cf12b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F20%2F145222_11c6099c10fc2ed7207bcae46a7cf12b.jpeg&h=161cfadf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uplo